00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
 I'm thirsty for ....: Homemade cider 

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.500
 You need to: 

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.600
 Granny Smith and red apples- 12 

00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:09.700
 Oranges of Valencia- 1 

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.500
 Brown sugar 225g 

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.600
 Nutmeg 1 whole 

00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:17.700
 Cinnamon 4 sticks 

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:19.800
 Cloves 1 tablespoon 

00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:21.400
 cooking pot 

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:23.000
 Strainer 

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.500
 Potato masher 

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.000
 and stamen 

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.000
 Clean and cut the fruits 

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.500
 ... and put them in the pan 

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.500
 do not forget the sugar! 

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.000
 Put the spices in the cheesecloth 

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.000
 Close the property! 

00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:56.100
 This will give you all the flavor without the small pieces 

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
 Cover with water 

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:07.000
 Boil and cover for at least an hour 

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.000
 Crush the fruits 

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:17.500
 Simmer again for two hours 

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.000
 When it's over let cool completely 

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:27.000
 Put a strainer and a stamen on a bowl 

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:40.000
 Squeeze all these delights! 

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.000
 Salud! 

